divs: Sighting Details Walking home, people in street asked me if I knewWHAT it was? they were looking up. I said nothing and looked. It did notmove. Blue light likeflame, pulsating, never moving for almost an hour. A fewtimes it dimed to nothing and came back again. A few times it flickered like aflourscense light. It was below the clouds and a southern star was visible
Summary: bright,blue,glowing, light high in sky, pulsating
